title: My Enemy, My Friend
description: The Ice Emperor's terrible Ice Dragon strikes again, laying waste to the Ice Fisher's village, forcing the ninja to go after Lloyd…

title: Worship
description: When the Fashionistas unveil their new mind controlling perfume, the Powerpuff Girls must find a way to stop them before Townsville falls under their spell.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: #Retirada
description: Jessica Cruz y algunas de sus mejores amigas salen a pasar una noche de campamento sin sus poderes, iy son atacadas por Hiedra Venenosa y una horda de plantas zombis!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Nostalgia Is Not a Substitute for an Actual Story
description: The Titans time travel back to the 1980s to determine whether or not it was the best decade ever.

title: El Comienzo de Cobrangutan
description: Mao Mao incita a Cobrangután y a los Piratas del Cielo a convertirse en villanos verdaderamente malvados, dignos de un héroe legendario como él.

title: Mama a la Orden
description: Con el deseo de tener la experiencia de una madre, los osos usan una aplicación que les traerá una madre a la puerta de sus casas.

title: Skips Strikes
description: Skips reveals himself to be an excellent bowler, until he realizes he has to bowl Death's team.

title: James II
description: Finn and Jake discover Clone James has been faking his own death to collect medals. But there are 25 Jameses running amok!

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Mr. Smoothy's
description: The Plumbers' resident geniuses, Blukic and Driba set off to find some smoothies meanwhile Ben and Rook try to stop Trombipulor from gaining the source of absolute power.

title: Double Cross
description: Batman has Plastic Man disguise himself as Two-Face in order to set a trap for Deadshot. Unfortunately things get complicated when the real Two-Face escapes custody.

title: Drilling Deep
description: At school, Aki struggles with the side effects of his newly replicated Drill Man schematics; later, as Mega Man, he learns to control his Fire Powers in thwarting Drill Man's assault on Skyraisers Inc.

title: Escandalosos
description: Los Osos bebé se inscriben en un torneo de lucha libre mexicana.

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Villains in a Van Getting Gelato
description: Four of the Titans' greatest villains reminisce about past incidents and recall how the Titans wronged them.

title: The Space Beam
description: The new rulers of Plun-Darr say they'll bring one of the Mutants home; whichever one of them activates a homing beacon that will blow up the Thundercats. Now it's every Mutant for themselves as they battle it out to be the one to activate the beacon!

title: ThunderDogs
description: The Thundercats agree to foster a demonic puppy from the Astral Plane until they can find it the perfect owner. But could the perfect owner be their worst enemy? Their worst enemy is Mumm-Ra in case you forgot!

title: Reststop Roustabout
description: With the Rustbucket stopped on the Midwest roadside, Ben locks himself inside with his tablet as Max and Gwen enjoy the great outdoors, until Team Tennyson is pulled into a wild Jack-a-Lope chase.

title: La Invitacion
description: Craig y sus amigos están invitados a una exclusiva merienda con deliciosos postres, si es que pueden quedarse hasta el final de la fiesta.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Cowbar Jones: Origines
description: Pardo presenta la precuela de su película de Crowbar Jones a Nom Nom, con la esperanza de que acepte actuar en la película.

title: Catfight
description: The princesses Looma and Attea are at odds over who gets to marry Ben!

title: The Galactic Enforcers
description: Ben joins a trio of intergalactic alien heroes tracking down the bounty hunter Six Six. But this bunch of heroes is not all it's cracked up to be.

title: Sidekick Scouts
description: KO gets more than he bargained for when he gets a sidekick.

title: Un Gran Enfrentamiento
description: Lightning por fin revela la ubicación de la Célula Núcleo, pero cuando Los Fantásticos llegan, descubren que Magnus fue más rápido que ellos.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: La Ultima Cambia Formas
description: Akita cuenta la historia de "la Elección" y cómo es que ella y su hermano gemelo, Kataru, fueron al bosque para descubrir su forma animal.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Strange Nedfellows
description: Omnibus hires the Warriors to get a one-of-a-kind salmon for his fancy aquarium, but Neddy joins them on their quest and wants the "Queen Sal," yet Man Fish the Fish Man wants the salmon to stay in the Fickle Sea!

title: Cambiando Objetos
description: Axel y el equipo luchan contra la Princesa SugarSalt por la posesión del martillo de Bearbarian, que le vendió uno de los suyos: iGalileo!

title: Just Wait in the Car
description: As Mary runs errands, Clarence waits in the car and struggles to fight boredom.

title: A Domar Los Cielos Peligrosos
description: Con el ala del avión no tripulado de Axel roto, el equipo debe encontrar otra forma de detener a Madcap y sus secuaces mientras se lanzan a los cielos en aviones de juguete para un asalto aéreo en el parque de la ciudad.

title: Mao Mao's Bike Adventure
description: When Mao Mao underestimates enemy and friend alike, it almost costs him the entire kingdom.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Triquicornio
description: Un misterioso pariente, el tío Triquicornio, aparece inesperadamente asegurando ser de la familia. Halcondrilo cree que solo son Master Frown y Brock en un disfraz de burro tratando de arruinar las cosas, pero Unikitty y Perricornio están convencidos de que Triquicornio en un viejo miembro de la familia. Halcondrilo sigue sus instintos de guardaespaldas e intenta probar que Triquicornio es un impostor.

title: The Sunflower
description: Our Trio makes a new friend in the Creek, but when her pet befalls a tragic fate, Kelsey believes she knows how to help.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Battle for the Bottled City
description: Atom shrinks Superman so he can visit his fellow Kryptonians in the bottled city of Kandor. Soon after, Brainiac attacks and takes off with the bottle. Atom is forced to take control of one of Superman's damaged robots in order to follow after Brainiac and retrieve the city.

title: Shock & AWW
description: When Courtney gets the old, gross daycare carpet replaced with a new one, the resulting static electricity has unexpected consequences.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: #AllyCat Part 2
description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

title: Gyranoide del Futuro
description: Manzana y Cebollín se esfuerzan por subir a la montaña rusa más loca del parque de diversiones.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Safari Sa'Bad
description: On their trip to Adrenaworld West, Ben takes a detour on a jungle cruise and finds himself hunted by the evil Tim Buktu. Our hero must outwit the baddie if he wants to make it off the amusement park ride alive!

title: Salsa Picante
description: La búsqueda de su salsa picante favorita hace que los Osos se involucren en una operación de picadura.

title: Orangusnake Begins
description: Mao Mao goads Orangusnake and the Sky Pirates into becoming truly terrible villains worthy of a legendary hero such as himself.

title: El cuarto oscuro
description: Tras ser rechazado por un club de fotografía, Val intenta conseguir una foto del legendario Chupacabra para demostrar su valor.

title: Nightmare Hospital
description: Steven and Connie sneak into a hospital to recover Rose's Sword.

title: Little Brother
description: Shelby is thrust into a new role after a party-related accident.

title: Bedtime Stories
description: When Puppycorn can't fall asleep, Dr. Fox uses an invention to bring classic bedtime stories to life. But the gang's presence leads to some surprising twists in these popular tales.

title: Three Girls and a Monster/Monkey See, Doggy Two
description: Three Girls and a Monster: The girls are once again in a furious battle with a ferocious monster. But Blossom and Buttercup can't agree on how to fight the beast and Bubbles just wants everyone to get along./Monkey See, Doggy Two: Mojo has discovered a fatal flaw in his brilliant plan and decides to reenact it step-by-step. The girls think they're experiencing deja vu but it's really just Mojo working his maniacal mischief.

title: Mr. Universe
description: Greg takes Steven on the road to find the origins of the Universe name.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Date with Gus
description: When Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve accidentally ruin Mr. Gus' night, the two of them go undercover as Mr. Gus's date.

title: Jermaine
description: After a chilling dream encounter, Finn & Jake are determined to reconnect with their reclusive brother.

title: The Gauntlet Part 1
description: Lord Obsidian unites the Robot Masters against Mega Man and his family for an epic showdown at the Lighthouse.

title: Bad Man Oldman
description: When the Warriors re-thatch Old Man Oldman's roof and absentmindedly make it look like Prohyas' hair, Oldman dons an giant evil toupee exacts his revenge!

title: Fideito
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben seguir teniendo la onda suficiente para aparecer en el video musical de su rapero favorito.

title: Diversion Cuantica
description: Robin lleva a los demás Titanes a un viaje a través del vertiginoso mundo de la física cuántica.

title: Gettin' Twiggy with It/Cop Out
description: Getting' Twiggy with It: Mitch takes Twiggy, the class hamster, home for the weekend. But when Mitch flushes Twiggy down the toilet, he emerges bigger and badder than ever./Cop Out: A lazy Townsville cop gets fired and blames the girls for saving the day too often, thereby stealing his job. Now, it's payback time and he has the perfect plan to stop those pint-size punks.

title: The Vase
description: Sick of Granny Jojo's ugly gifts, Nicole encourages the kids to take matters into their own hands and accidentally break her latest hideous vase. But when Gumball, Darwin and Anais try to destroy it, they discover it is more robust than it seems.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: A Fragile Hope
description: Having discovered the terrible truth of Zane's fate, Lloyd finds himself imprisoned and alone in the clutches of the Ice Emperor.

title: The Price of Advice
description: After a paper origami fortune teller tells Izzy she's the world's best advice giver, she's determined to prove it.

title: Dendy's Video Channel
description: Dendy tries to update KO's Video Channel for him, but has trouble finding something to post.

title: Lil' Mac
description: Mr. Gus' nephew terrorizes Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve.

title: Throwing Shade Part 2
description: Mega Man stops Fire Man by replicating his powers and fighting fire with fire. Unfortunately, Mega Man also learns that he can replicate a robot's mental state as well, and must get his own anger under control to win. Defeated, Fire Man reports back to his secret master, Sgt. Night!

title: Hot Sauce
description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: El sentimiento
description: Mientras Max y Gwen se deleitan en el espíritu navideño de Winter Wonderland, Ben no podría estar más aburrido y concentrado en los juguetes. Pero cuando los Weatherheads fijan sus miras en Winter Wonderland como su próximo objetivo, nuestro héroe debe conectarse con sus emociones si quiere salvar la ciudad.

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Oportunidades Laborales
description: Después de derrotar a Magnus, los Fantásticos reciben una oferta de empleo de alguien inesperado... Filomena Dusk.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ayudantes Scouts
description: KO obtiene más de lo que esperaba cuando consigue su propio ayudante.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Exquisite Grandpa
description: Uncle Grandpa has been having some truly bizarre night terrors.

title: El precio de un consejo
description: Cuando una esfera de la fortuna de origami le dice a Izzy que es la mejor consejera de vida del mundo, está decidida a probar que es así.

title: Too Much of a Goo'd Thing
description: Beth refuses to believe that the adorable goo creature she's created out of slime is consuming the kids until she and Gwen are the only two left in class.

title: The Worst
description: Each member of the family thinks their demographic has it the toughest. Gumball and Darwin think guys have it the worst.  Mom thinks women do.  Anais thinks kids do.  And Dad thinks that grown-ups do. They decide the only way to figure it out is to spend a day in each other's shoes, no matter if they're too-small, too-big, or high-heeled.

title: Witchy Simone Ruins Everything!
description: Witchy Simone joins Witch Way, but Gateaux is the odd cat out so he hires the Warriors to break up Witchy Simone and Morbidia and defeat a mission that has King Rexxtopher hopping mad!

title: Missing Cat
description: When Chelsea accidentally lets her pet cat Crumbles out, the cat goes missing! Reluctant to ask for help, she struggles to find the cat before anyone realizes it's gone. It's up to cat whisperer Clarence to interject and find Crumbles, whether Chelsea wants his help or not!

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Shirt Club
description: Steven and Buck Dewey make t-shirts together.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: Doctor Visit
description: Uncle Grandpa hates going to the doctor but he's overdue for an important vaccination.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Sonrie y Aguanta
description: Cuando un dolor de muelas envía a Axel al dentista, el equipo debe luchar contra la Princesa SugarSalt, quien confunde la nueva "corona" de Axel con la realidad.

title: The Last of the Formlings
description: Akita tells the story of the "Choosing" and how she, and her twin brother, Kataru, went into the wilds to discover their animal forms.

title: Madtrap
description: Madcap and Princess SugarSalt trap Axel and the team inside a Minergy-powered labyrinth that attacks them with their greatest fears, forcing them to work together and escape as a unit.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: El Oso
description: In a flashback to long ago, Charlie has an adventure in the Mexican desert.

title: My Name Is Jose
description: The Titans have Raven give them new super powers but have a hard time adjusting.

title: El Coleccionista
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic pierde una de las preciadas monedas de Val, Val hace un trato con un misterioso coleccionista de antigüedades para reemplazarla, pero el trato tiene consecuencias terribles.

title: The Kid From 3030
description: The kids meet a mysterious kid from the future and try to help him complete his mission.

title: Corruption
description: The story of Zane's arrival in the Never-Realm and how he fell under the sway of the villainous Vex.

title: Craig World
description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

title: El ProtocoloKaiju
description: De vuelta en la ciudad de Ninjago, Wu y Pixal intentan localizar el Reino del Jamás y liberan accidentalmente a una temida criatura del Reino de los Muertos.

title: Joshua & Margaret Investigations
description: Finn and Jake's parents hunt an unearthly menace in the woods.

title: Garden of Evil
description: Poison Ivy takes control of Swamp Thing using his vegetative powers to overwhelm Gotham with dangerous plants.

title: Officer Moody
description: Pieces of Mr. Reese's past are revealed when his old partner on the police force, Officer Moody, visits Aberdale Elementary.

title: Positive Attitude Theory
description: Apple and Onion spend a day in Falafel's shoes and use their positive attitude to prove he shouldn't be so grumpy.

title: La Aventura de la Moto de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao subestima por igual a sus enemigos y a sus amigos, por poco le cuesta el reino entero.

title: Slam Dunk
description: Mordecai needs access to the computer so he and Rigby challenge Muscle Man and High Five Ghost to a basketball game for a week's worth of computer time.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Mi Enemigo, Mi Amigo
description: El terrible Dragón de Hielo del Emperador ataca de nuevo, arrasando la aldea de los Pescadores de Hielo, obligando a los ninjas a seguir los pasos de Lloyd.

title: Sr. Universo
description: Greg lleva a Steven de viaje para encontrar los orígenes del nombre del Universo.

title: Rap It Up
description: Mordecai and Rigby don't want Pops to be called a loser so they say that they'll join him in a rap battle.

title: Green with Envy
description: When the local news interviews Uncle Andrew about his toy inventing, an envious Galileo stages a play in the park with the help of Axel and the team, only to be interrupted by an equally envious Madcap - out to steal the spotlight for himself!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Teoria de Actitud Positiva
description: Manzana y Cebollín pasan un día en los zapatos de Falafel y usan su actitud positiva para demostrar que no debería estar tan malhumorado.

title: Una Fragil Esperanza
description: Después de descubrir la terrible verdad del destino de Zane, Lloyd se encuentra en el calabozo, en las garras del Emperador de Hielo.

title: The Boy Who Cried Lechuza
description: After faking an injury to get out of work, Vic gains sympathy from everyone while unknowingly attracting attention from a dangerous mythical creature.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Corrupcion
description: Conoceremos la historia de la llegada de Zane al Reino del Jamás y cómo cayó bajo el dominio del villano Vex.

title: Hot Air Buffoon/Ploys R' Us
description: Hot Air Buffoon: The Mayor realizes the girls are doing all the work in his city for him. So he mans a hot air balloon and starts fighting crime the old-fashioned way./Ploys R' Us: The girls wake up to find their room filled with toys. They soon figure out that the Professor has been sleepwalking and stealing. Instead of reporting it, the girls take advantage of the situation.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Long Skate Home
description: After they get accused of a crime they didn't commit, the Powerpuff girls and the Derbytantes have to find a way to clear their name!

title: La Aventura de Lightning
description: Lightning descubre la Célula Núcleo enterrada bajo tierra, y se enfrenta a Strata El Cazador para intentar proteger su secreto.

title: El Oso
description: En flashes retrospectivos al pasado lejano, vemos una aventura de Charlie en el desierto mexicano.

title: Replaced
description: Mordecai and Rigby find out that Benson is going to replace them and have to figure out a way to stop it.

title: Grin and Bear It
description: When a toothache sends Axel to the dentist, the team must fight off Princess SugarSalt, who confuses Axel's new "crown" for the real thing.

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: There Are No Hoppy Endings
description: Chef struggles to maintain his sanity when the kids continue to blame a stuffed rabbit named Hoppy for everything they do wrong.

title: El chico del 3030
description: Los niños conocen a un misterioso niño del futuro y tratan de ayudarlo a completar su misión.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: A Real Steal/Lightning Unleashed
description: A Real Steal: Dan embarks on a solo adventure to outdo Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers and winds up having to be saved by them instead./Lightning Unleashed: Lightning uncovers the Mind Core Cell buried beneath the Earth and battles Stata the Hunter in an effort to protect its secret.

title: La Trampa de Madcap
description: Madcap y Princess SugarSalt atrapan a Axel y al equipo dentro de un laberinto impulsado por Minergy que los ataca con sus mayores temores, obligándolos a trabajar juntos y escapar como una unidad.

title: #ScrambledEggs
description: It's egg-xactly what you think: the home economics "Egg-Baby" assignment, where students are paired up and given an egg to "care for" over a weekend. But when tragedy befalls egg after egg, what should be an easy assignment escalates into a madcap romp with super-high stakes!

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple helps Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Growing Pains
description: Puppycorn is sick of Unikitty always helping him out and doesn't want to be the "little" brother anymore, so he uses some of Dr Fox's 'grow taffy' to grow literally bigger than Unikitty. Meanwhile, a black hole is on its way to destroy the planet. But when Puppycorn takes too much and continues growing, he starts accidentally destroying the kingdom. Unikitty takes grow taffy and grows big as well to help out, but when they're both the size of planets, Puppycorn proves he can take care of himself on his own by destroying the black hole and saving the kingdom.

title: The Trade
description: After accidentally trading away Chad's favorite baseball card, Clarence has to trade it back! Determined to become an expert, Clarence transforms himself into a slick salesman, before facing the ultimate deal.

title: #DramaQueen
description: Oliver Queen must face off against his greatest rival yet, Mortimer Drake, while Green Arrow also finds himself up against a new foe, The Cavalier.

title: The Kaiju Protocol
description: Back in Ninjago City, Wu and Pixal attempt to locate the Never-Realm, and accidentally unleash a dreaded creature from the Departed Realm…

title: Me Llamo Jose
description: Raven les da nuevos superpoderes a los Titanes, pero a ellos les cuesta adaptarse.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Victor y la Lechuza
description: Después de fingir una lesión para no tener que trabajar, Vic se gana la compasión de todos mientras que, sin saberlo, atrae la atención de una peligrosa criatura mítica.

title: Bros in Space
description: Rook brings Ben to his home planet to meet the family. Unbeknownst to them, an old foe is raising an army to steal the planet's most precious resource!  (Introducing Rook's family.)

title: Full Grown Pizza
description: Uncle Grandpa makes it hard for Pizza Steve to prove he's not a baby.

title: The Uncle
description: Gumball and Darwin are desperate to meet Ocho's famous uncle.

title: Kitty & Hawk
description: When Puppycorn's favorite toy goes missing, Unikitty & Hawkodile team up to track down the thief, buddy-cop style! But when things get tough and the case goes cold, now it's not just their partnership on the line, but their friendship!

title: #GatoCallejero Parte 1
description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Demasiada baba
description: Beth se niega a creer que la adorable criatura de baba que ha creado con limo esté comiéndose a los niños hasta que ella y Gwen son las únicas dos que quedan en la clase.

title: #AllyCat Part 1
description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

title: Un Triunfo Robado
description: Dan se embarca en una aventura para superar al nuevo equipo de Peleadores Bakugan de Magnus, pero al final, ellos lo salvarán a él.

title: Say Uncle
description: A long lost relative of Steven's comes to town to aid him in unlocking the power of his mother's Gem!

title: La Nostalgia No Es Un Substituto Para Una Historia Moderna
description: iLos Titanes viajan en el tiempo hasta los años 80 para determinar si realmente fue la mejor década de la historia!

title: To Tame the Perilous Skies!
description: With Axel's drone-wing broken, the team must find another way to stop Madcap and his minions as they take to the skies in toy airplanes for an aerial assault on the city park.

title: Mini Mongor

title: Dolores del crecimiento

title: #HuevosRevueltos
description: Gracias a la tarea de la clase de Economía Domestica, los estudiantes son emparejados y se les entrega un huevo para "cuidar" durante el fin de semana. Pero cuando la tragedia acontece huevo tras huevo, lo que debería ser una tarea fácil, ise convierte en una disparatada persecución!

title: Small World: Stone Cold Spider Part 2

title: #Retreat!
description: Jessica Cruz and some super friends go on an overnight camping trip without their powers and are attacked by Poison Ivy and a horde of Plant Zombies!

title: Red Action 3: Grudgement Day
description: KO and Enid attempt to prevent a mysterious power battle between Rad and Red Action.

title: The Singing
description: The town of Elmore becomes an all-singing, all-dancing mash up. Everyone has a song inside them, but do they really need to be heard?

title: Escandalosos

title: Tygra's Garden

title: Jefe por un dia
description: Cuando Chata deja que Vic sea el jefe del puesto de tacos por un día, él decide despedir a Val, lo que trae consecuencias desastrosas.

title: Manzana es Bajito

title: That's the Stuff
description: While touring a space museum, Ben's excitement multiplies when he learns that recently discovered space stuff is being examined inside the museum's lab. Once the stuff comes to life and the shape-shifting goo replicates our hero, Ben must look within if he is to stop the case of mistaken identity.

title: Los Safaris son Malos
description: En su paseo a Adrenaworld West, Ben toma un desvío por una selva y descubre que lo persigue el malvado Tim Buktu. iNuestro héroe debe ser más listo que el villano si quiere llegar al parque de diversiones con vida!

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Inside Job

title: #LaReinaDelDrama
description: Oliver Queen debe enfrentarse al mayor rival al que jamás se haya enfrenado, Mortimer Drake, mientras Green Arrow se encuentra con un nuevo enemigo.

description: Luego de que la Célula Núcleo pusiera en estado de hibernación a los Bakugan de ambos equipos, Dan y Magnus se encuentran atrapados en una batalla donde lo apostarán todo.

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: The Re-Run
description: When we last saw Gumball, he was hitting rewind on Rob's Universal Remote just in time to save himself from being trapped in The Void. The remote has now taken Gumball back to the beginning of that disastrous day. Armed with the knowledge of what this day has in store, he must try and stop Rob from destroying his life.

title: Swampy Johnny
description: The Thundercats invite a super cool swamp man into the Cat's Lair who is on the run from some scary looking aliens!

originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Dark Room

title: The Collector
description: When Vic accidentally loses one of Val's prized coins Val makes a deal with a mysterious antiques collector to replace it, but the deal has terrible consequences.

title: Dunklecorn
description: A mysterious relative, Uncle Donklecorn, shows up unexpectedly, claiming to be family. Hawkodile thinks it's just Master Frown and Brock in a donkey costume, trying to ruin things as usual, but Unikitty and Puppycorn are convinced Donklecorn is an old family member. Hawk follows his bodyguard senses and tries to prove that Donklecorn is a fake, until finally the real Master Frown and Brock show up and ruin things, just as he suspected they would. He admits he was wrong about Uncle Donklecorn, but all is forgiven and the friends dance it out together.

title: Carrie

title: The Last Kid in the Creek

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.

title: #GatoCallejero Parte 2

originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Carrie

title: Sarah

description: Dr. Fox accidentally transports the gang inside her brain, where they must control her movements to complete a dangerous experiment.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: The Feels

title: KO, Rad, and Enid!
description: When confronted with their lack of a team gimmick, KO, Rad, and Enid wonder what their group identity should be.

title: El ultimo nino en el Arroyo
description: Por una terrible maldición, Craig se convierte en el único niño del Arroyo.

description: Ben and Kevin 11 are beamed up to a space ship where must learn to battle together in order to bring down a vicious alien fight promoter.

title: AbaracaDuncan
description: When a magic trick goes sideways, Duncan makes a great escape and Harold becomes the target of a Sorcerer Hunt!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Gyranoid of the Future
description: Apple and Onion struggle to ride Gyranoid of the Future, the craziest roller coaster at the carnival.

title: Public Radio
description: After listening to a public radio broadcast during class, Clarence is inspired to record a radio interview of his own featuring his buddy Sumo. When Ms. Baker hears the charming interview, she calls in a favor and gets Clarence a spot on the actual Aberdale Public Radio! The search is on - to find the perfect interview subject for his big day.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol

title: Primogenita

originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

description: When KO finds moments of his life slipping by, he begins to suspect something weird is going on.

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: Un Nuevo Empleo
description: Durante un comercial para celebrar su contrato con el equipo AAAnimus, Dan y Los Fantásticos deciden rebelarse antes que traicionar sus principios.

description: Ronaldo does some investigative reporting on whether Steven and the Crystal Gems are safe for Beach City.

title: Efectos en Cuatro Colores
description: Axel, Galileo y Sarge son transportados por Minergy por Madcap a las páginas del cómic favorito de Axel, cuyo héroe resulta no ser tan genial después de todo.

title: The Headsucker's Moxy/Equal Fights
description: The Headsucker's Moxy: There's a mysterious villain in town who's sucking pertinent information from the brains of powerful people and committing crimes. How do the girls trap this sucker before his next victim is drained?/Equal Fights: When the girls try to catch a local female villain, she tells them that as women they've got to stick together. It's up to the women of Townsville to teach our heroines the true meaning of equality.

title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

title: La Naturaleza de las Cosas
description: Mientras pasean por el Parque Nacional Geyser Gulch, el trío Tennyson descubre un generador a vapor de Steam Smyth y debe apagarlo antes de que sobrecargue la red eléctrica o, peor, icause un terremoto masivo que destruya el parque entero!

title: Es la cosa
description: Mientras visita un museo espacial, la emoción de Ben se multiplica cuando se entera de que están examinando en el laboratorio unas "cosas espaciales" que acaban de descubrir. Pero cuando esa cosa viscosa cobra vida y comienza a replicar a nuestro héroe con su capacidad de cambiar de forma, Ben debe buscar en su interior si quiere detener el caso de identidad equivocada.

title: The Gauntlet Part 2
description: As Dr. Light and Suna turn the Robot Masters against each other, Mega Man defeats and unmasks his arch nemeses, Lord Obsidian, who turns out to be Sgt. Night in disguise, and finally learns the identity of Namagem, Mega Man's long lost twin brother!

title: Parada de Descanso

title: Action Comedy
description: Rhyboflaven's local fictional superhero, Broccoli Punch, has an all-new, spectacular action stage show, but when Flonk masquerades as the star, the Warriors disguise themselves as broccoli bad guys to teach the imposter a lesson!

title: I Am Chair
description: During a stressful trip to the mall, Robin finds peace in a massage chair.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
Kitty y Halcon: Protectores de la Ley
description: Cuando el juguete favorito de Perricornio desaparece, Unikitty y Halcondrilo se unen para localizar al ladrón, ial estilo socios policías! Pero cuando las cosas se ponen difíciles y el caso no se resuelve, ya no es solo su sociedad la que está en juego, sino también su amistad.

title: Throwing Shade Part 1

title: The Invitation
description: Craig and his friends are invited to an exclusive tea party with delicious desserts, if they can last to the end of the party.

title: Breakpoint

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Nueva Mascota

title: Iron & Stone

title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.

title: The Nature of Things
description: While sightseeing at the Geyser Gulch National Park, the Tennyson trio uncover Steam Smythe's steam-powered generator and must shut it down before it overloads the power grid or, even worse, causes a massive earthquake that destroys the entire park!
